# CONTACT FORM

### Submit a contact form
POST http://localhost:5000/api/contact
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Doe",
  "email": "jane@example.com",
  "subject": "Asking for scholarship",
  "message": "I would like to know more about your services."
}

### Get all contact form submissions
GET http://localhost:5000/api/contact

### Get a contact form submission by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/contact/CONTACT_ID_HERE

### Update a contact form submission
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/contact/CONTACT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Jane Smith",
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com",
  "message": "Updated message."
}

### Delete a contact form submission
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/contact/CONTACT_ID_HERE


# STUDENT ROUTES

### Create a new student
POST http://localhost:5000/api/students
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "surname": "Marco",
  "firstName": "Justine Jynne",
  "middleName": "A.",
  "lastSchoolYearAttended": "2020-2023",
  "courseOrStrand": "Grade 7",
  "presentAddress": "sampaloc",
  "contactNumber": "09123456789",
  "emailAddress": "justine@gmail.com"
}

### Get all students
GET http://localhost:5000/api/students

### Get a student by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/students/6827ef3ee4e6fb2501433626

### Update a student
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/students/STUDENT_ID_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Johnathan Doe",
  "email": "johnathan@example.com"
}

### Delete a student
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/students/6827efc9e4e6fb250143362b


